  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Empathy is an important skill to learn for medical student. However, learning empathy remain
      difficult. The investigators aim was to assess the efficacy of a specific training, Balint
      like, on the empathy abilities of medical students in the 4th year. The investigators planned
      a randomized controlled trial in 3 universities.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
